assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:41:51.000Z","msg":"而且警隊嘅福份好過其他紀律部隊<br />\n警隊有自己嘅警務人員薪級表<br />\n自己部門嘅宿舍多過其他部門<br />\n分配到嘅紀律部隊宿舍又多過其他部門<br />\n仲有自己嘅康樂設施（警官會所 警察體育遊樂會）"},{"pid":"e7c04d3957a0a52fa9a4e138b7a8ae216ddde6c8","tid":2361754,"uid":168250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c70083fe8b7ab7d09a455d3136f331d633f54dbe","tid":2361754,"uid":168250,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c79c0ab0005af26988db5a88f9b794023143ba63","tid":2361754,"uid":117689,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:41:51.000Z","msg":"而且警隊嘅福份好過其他紀律部隊<br />\n警隊有自己嘅警務人員薪級表<br />\n自己部門嘅宿舍多過其他部門<br />\n分配到嘅紀律部隊宿舍又多過其他部門<br />\n仲有自己嘅康樂設施（警官會所 警察體育遊樂會）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:42:23.000Z","msg":"*福利"},{"pid":"006b466d161830fdc7e596540a92a82294aa5622","tid":2361754,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6f1eb5eefd4b2657bccaf9c1a64c0887958cca3","tid":2361754,"uid":34755,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:17:19.000Z","msg":"粉嶺幾好呀 去浩園咁近"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"拜山唔使擇日"},{"pid":"206b2c2020da629ff4f20375daa42ddca3f787bc","tid":2361754,"uid":168250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c9f3dae2498737a4a83cb16a72dddb1758ded8a","tid":2361754,"uid":117689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9869ee8b7365e41b374840ff19f95d3844ecbb5b","tid":2361754,"uid":168250,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"c79c0ab0005af26988db5a88f9b794023143ba63","tid":2361754,"uid":117689,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:38:20.000Z","msg":"政府覺得佢地職務多 工作時間長 但係人工比文職職系 專業職系低 所以福利比其他公務員好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"咁就數返88年凌衛理委員會 當時份報告話警隊係政府嘅最終執法機關（the agency of last resort）係唯一緊急紀律部隊 要保持警隊政治中立就要有良好嘅待遇 簡單黎講就係籠絡人心<br />\n<br />\n所以報告建議設警務人員薪級表同一般紀律人員薪級表 分開警隊同其他紀律部隊 警察部嘅福利係好過其他部隊好多<br />\n<br />\n其他部隊一直都爭取緊提升地位同警隊睇齊 但唔成功"}]}